                  "revisionId": 2652395,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Unlike Anemic Agility and Vile Acceleration , Frail Momentum gives the same amount of fire rate as the non-corrupt equivalent, Shotgun Barrage . As such, Frail Momentum should only be used in conjunction with Shotgun Barrage in builds aiming to maximize fire rate."
                }
