                  "revisionId": 2652395,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The negative damage boost is additive with other damage boosting mods such as Point Blank . Combining a maxed Point Blank (+90% damage) with Frail Momentum will result in a total damage bonus of +75%."
                }
              },
